# Project Scope Changes towards "Sports Talent Assessment"

To transition this project strictly into an **"AI Powered Mobile Platform For Democratizing Sports Talent Assessment"** and focus solely on this domain, several "fitness companion" features should be removed, and core features should be repurposed to serve athletic evaluation instead of general workouts.

Here is the breakdown of the changes that need to be made:

## 1. Features to Remove completely
These features are too focused on general health/fitness and do not fit an objective "talent assessment" platform.
*   **Nutrition Tracking**:
    *   **Backend**: Delete [controllers/nutritionController.js](file:///c:/Users/Admin/Downloads/reio-main/backend/controllers/nutritionController.js), [routes/nutrition.js](file:///c:/Users/Admin/Downloads/reio-main/backend/routes/nutrition.js), [models/NutritionLog.js](file:///c:/Users/Admin/Downloads/reio-main/backend/models/NutritionLog.js).
    *   **Frontend**: Delete [pages/NutritionPage.jsx](file:///c:/Users/Admin/Downloads/reio-main/frontend/src/pages/NutritionPage.jsx).
    *   **Routing/Nav**: Remove all nutrition links from [App.jsx](file:///c:/Users/Admin/Downloads/reio-main/frontend/src/App.jsx) and [components/Navbar.jsx](file:///c:/Users/Admin/Downloads/reio-main/frontend/src/components/Navbar.jsx).
*   **Daily Motivation / Quotes**:
    *   **Backend**: Delete [controllers/motivationController.js](file:///c:/Users/Admin/Downloads/reio-main/backend/controllers/motivationController.js), [routes/motivation.js](file:///c:/Users/Admin/Downloads/reio-main/backend/routes/motivation.js).
    *   **Frontend**: Remove any motivation widgets from [DashboardPage.jsx](file:///c:/Users/Admin/Downloads/reio-main/frontend/src/pages/DashboardPage.jsx).

## 2. Features to Repurpose & Rename
Terms like "Workout" and general fitness tracking should be replaced with "Assessment", "Drills", and "Talent Metrics".
*   **Workouts -> Assessments**:
    *   **Frontend**: Rename [WorkoutPage.jsx](file:///c:/Users/Admin/Downloads/reio-main/frontend/src/pages/WorkoutPage.jsx) to `AssessmentPage.jsx`. Update the route in [App.jsx](file:///c:/Users/Admin/Downloads/reio-main/frontend/src/App.jsx) to `/assessment`.
    *   **Frontend UI**: Update [ExerciseDemo.jsx](file:///c:/Users/Admin/Downloads/reio-main/frontend/src/components/ExerciseDemo.jsx) to focus on standard sports talent combines/drills (e.g., Vertical Jump, 40-yard dash, Agility Cone Drills) rather than general gym exercises like squats or bench presses.
*   **Session Management**:
    *   **Backend**: Update [models/Session.js](file:///c:/Users/Admin/Downloads/reio-main/backend/models/Session.js) and [controllers/sessionController.js](file:///c:/Users/Admin/Downloads/reio-main/backend/controllers/sessionController.js) to track "Assessment Sessions". The schema should capture drill types, AI-calculated scores (speed, explosive power, mechanics), and talent percentiles rather than calories burned or reps.
*   **User Profiles & Onboarding**:
    *   **Frontend**: Update [ProfileSetupPage.jsx](file:///c:/Users/Admin/Downloads/reio-main/frontend/src/pages/ProfileSetupPage.jsx) and [ProfilePage.jsx](file:///c:/Users/Admin/Downloads/reio-main/frontend/src/pages/ProfilePage.jsx) to collect athletic baseline data (e.g., Primary Sport, Position, Height, Weight, Wingspan) instead of general fitness goals (weight loss, muscle building).
    *   **Backend**: Update [models/User.js](file:///c:/Users/Admin/Downloads/reio-main/backend/models/User.js) to reflect athlete profiles.
*   **Dashboard**:
    *   **Frontend**: Overhaul [DashboardPage.jsx](file:///c:/Users/Admin/Downloads/reio-main/frontend/src/pages/DashboardPage.jsx) to display a "Talent Profile", showcasing the user's aggregate assessment scores, historical progress in specific athletic metrics, and AI recommendations for sport-specific improvements, replacing any charts related to generic fitness routines.

## 3. Configuration & Metadata
*   **Package.json**: Change the project name from `"name": "adaptive-fitness-companion"` to something like `"name": "sports-talent-assessment-app"`.
*   **AI Analysis Endpoint ([backend/routes/analyze.js](file:///c:/Users/Admin/Downloads/reio-main/backend/routes/analyze.js))**: Ensure the prompt and logic passed to the AI specifically contextualizes the user's data to generate a "Sports Talent Report" (evaluating biomechanics, explosiveness, form) rather than general workout feedback.
